summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department; authorizing the grant of an easement to King County for road and storm drain purposes over and along a portion of the City's East Side Supply Line right of way in Lots 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 and 6 in Block 1 of C. D. Hillman's Lake Washington Garden of Eden, Division No. 8, in the vicinity of the south end of Lake Boren, King County, Washington.
